				<descriptionOfRestrictions xml:lang="en">At present, the main technology used to produce industrial silicon in China is the reduction of industrial silicon with carbonaceous reducing agent</descriptionOfRestrictions>
				<descriptionOfRestrictions xml:lang="zh">现阶段国内工业硅制取主要釆用的工艺是碳质还原剂对工业硅进行还原</descriptionOfRestrictions>
