		<technology>
			<technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesses xml:lang="en">The carbonaceous reducing agent is used to reduce industrial silicon</technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesses>
			<technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesses xml:lang="zh">碳质还原剂对工业硅进行还原</technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesses>
			<technologicalApplicability xml:lang="en">The industrial silicon described is produced at 99% purity using a carbon reduction method, and is mainly utilized for the extraction of multi-crystalline silicon (multi-Si) employed as raw material in the photovoltaic industry for solar energy applications.</technologicalApplicability>
			<technologicalApplicability xml:lang="zh">所描述的工业硅通过碳质还原法生产，纯度为99%，主要用于提取作为太阳能光伏行业用途的多晶硅（multi-Si）原料。</technologicalApplicability>
			<referenceToTechnologyFlowDiagrammOrPicture type="source data set" refObjectId="37664184-e5bb-621d-b50e-25235aef307e" uri="../sources/37664184-e5bb-621d-b50e-25235aef307e.xml">
