			<referenceToDataSource type="source data set" refObjectId="c1afabe7-91c6-4590-a747-89aaf888091e" uri="../sources/c1afabe7-91c6-4590-a747-89aaf888091e.xml">
				<common:shortDescription xml:lang="en">何洋. 太阳能级多晶硅的生命周期评价. (西南交通大学, 2013).</common:shortDescription>
				<common:shortDescription xml:lang="zh">何洋. 太阳能级多晶硅的生命周期评价. (西南交通大学, 2013).</common:shortDescription>
			</referenceToDataSource>
			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="en">When using this data set for LCA, it is crucial to consider that the dataset represents current industrial silicon production levels using carbonaceous reducing agents within China. Inclusion of this dataset in LCA studies should consider technological applicability such as technological relevance to current production methods and geographic specificity. Due to the specificity of the data sourced from representative literature, the users must ensure that the dataset aligns well with the scope and boundaries of their particular LCA study, especially when considering solar-grade polysilicon. Users need to calculate the resource and energy inputs, as well as environmental emissions, for the life cycle of solar-grade multi-Si based on 1 kg units to maintain consistency and ensure accurate impact assessment.</useAdviceForDataSet>
			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="zh">在使用该数据集进行生命周期评估(LCA)时，重要的是考虑数据集代表了中国当前使用碳质还原剂的工业硅生产水平。将该数据集纳入LCA研究时应考虑技术适宜性，如与当前生产方法的技术相关性和地理特定性。由于数据来源于具有代表性的文献，用户必须确保数据集与其特定LCA研究的范围和边界线吻合，特别是当考虑太阳能级多晶硅时。用户需要基于1千克单位计算多晶硅生命周期过程的资源和能源输入以及环境排放，以保持一致性并确保准确的影响评估。</useAdviceForDataSet>
